## Scripts

Suggested package scripts (pnpm):

- `dev`: Vite dev server
- `build`: TypeScript typecheck and Vite build (`tsc -b && vite build`)
- `preview`: Vite preview
- `lint`: ESLint
- `lint:fix`: ESLint with auto-fix
- `format`: Prettier write
- `typecheck`: TypeScript type checking (`tsc -b`)
- `clean`: Remove dist, node_modules and prune pnpm store (`pnpm dlx rimraf dist node_modules pnpm store prune`)
- `test`: Run unit tests (`vitest run`) - Use Docker on Windows
- `test:watch`: Run unit tests in watch mode (`vitest`)
- `test:coverage`: Run unit tests with coverage (`vitest run --coverage`)
- `test:e2e`: Run e2e tests (Playwright)
- `docker:test`: Run unit tests with Docker (recommended on Windows)
- `docker:test:watch`: Run unit tests in watch mode with Docker
- `docker:test:e2e`: Run e2e tests with Docker

Place custom generators in `scripts/codegen.ts` and mock server in `scripts/mockServer.ts`.
